tfs $ autoreconf -i $ ./configure $ make\n\nAnd optionally, if you want to install it:\n\n    \n    \n    $ make install\n\n## About\n\nA bittorrent filesystem based on FUSE.\n\n### Topics\n\nmacos linux brew fuse debian bittorrent ubuntu filesystem libtorrent osxfuse\nbtfs\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nGPL-3.0 license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n3.2k stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n54 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n128 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\n25 tags\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Contributors 19\n\n\\+ 5 contributors\n\n## Languages\n\n  * C++ 84.6%\n  * Python 8.7%\n  * Shell 2.6%\n  * M4 2.2%\n  * Makefile 1.9%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": true}
